name: Doubutsu Chara Navi Uranai 2: Kosei Shinrigaku + Ren'ai Uranai Puzzle
overview: Doubutsu Chara Navi Uranai 2 - Kosei Shinri Gaku + Renai Uranai Puzzle is a puzzle game. Doubutsu Chara means Animal Fortune-telling. In the main part of the game the player can put a birthdate and the game will make a Animal-Fortune telling about love, luck, affinity, etc. The other part of the game is a puzzle game in which the player controls a goddess that will have to join different puzzle pieces to make a high score.
